<h2> 
CS 266 - Computational Geometry </h2>

<p>
Professor: 
<a href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~goodrich/">Michael T. Goodrich</a>, 
DBH 4216
<br>
Lectures: MWF 11:00-11:50, SST 220B
<br>
